  "content": "\n \n \n  <p><span></span></p><div data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space-collapse: collapse;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 0.578px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 28.4444px;visibility: visible;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><div data-id=\"85660\" data-custom=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" data-color=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: currentcolor;font-family: 微软雅黑;visibility: visible;\"><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 2em 0px 0px;padding: 0.5em 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;border-style: solid none;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);border-bottom-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);border-top-width: 1px;border-bottom-width: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: -1.2em 0px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;border-width: initial;border-style: initial;border-color: currentcolor;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);background-color: rgb(117, 117, 118);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;Datawhale干货&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n       <div data-style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: left;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 16px 16px 10px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: inherit;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 0px 5px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 12px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">教程：李沐，编辑：量子位</span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 16px 0px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space-collapse: collapse;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;color: rgb(73, 73, 73);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;visibility: visible;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-action-id=\"mdg1v2ei1m5a\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe js_wx_tap_highlight\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"Datawhale\" data-alias=\"Datawhale\" data-index=\"0\" data-from=\"2\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/vI9nYe94fsEXsBwQkpYLtE2vhn7Z3RVOSRu5M1VicIgqgMRKLsxsibK7OUSqUb1rUO4pfXnQyFYKqhryAIeh4MOg/300?wx_fmt=png&amp;wxfrom=19\" data-signature=\"一个专注于AI领域的开源组织，汇聚了众多优秀学习者，使命-for the learner，和学习者一起成长。\" data-id=\"MzIyNjM2MzQyNg==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-origin_num=\"792\" data-biz_account_status=\"0\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\">这一天，辣个男人终于回想起……他的小破站账号！</span><em style=\"font-style: normal;color: rgb(143, 143, 143);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\">（活久见）</span></em></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\">李沐</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">老师终</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\">于带着他的<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">手搓语音大模型教程回归了</span>….</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;visibility: visible;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100328256\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5324074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;padding: 0px;\" data-width=\"2880\" data-height=\"1534\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.xlab.app/img-proxy/?k=f7113d62&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYicUhk5aAGtClBf0EpJYZGRRarWCicQkpMb3yesdqm7ibRsXWEXvQRLmD6U2eiczXh6npuTPQBM3VnrOic5tskUlXuw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26randomid%3Dljqeq9m9\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\">本期视频不讲论文，李沐老师来手把手教大家怎样玩转他们团队最新研发的</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\">Higgs Audio V2模型</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\">，不仅能处理文本，还能同时理解并生成语音。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">除了一些常规语音任务外，这个模型还具备一些较为罕见的能力，比如生成多种语言的自然多说话人对话、旁白过程中的自动韵律调整、使用克隆声音进行旋律哼唱以及同时生成语音和背景音乐。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">整个过程堪称</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);\"><span leaf=\"\">“大力出奇迹”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，直接将</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);\"><span leaf=\"\">1000万小时</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">的语音数据整合到LLM的文本训练，让它能听也能说。</span><em style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\"><span leaf=\"\">（当然还有亿点点细节）</span></em></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: center;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100328254\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.24537037037037038\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;padding: 0px;\" data-width=\"1770\" data-height=\"434\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.xlab.app/img-proxy/?k=e677a9b7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYicUhk5aAGtClBf0EpJYZGRRarWCicQkpMyMZhe1V8Izh5ToyeqfuRZGf7ictMiaMGcED8KJcPN0KfslAzWQzf6pwA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26randomid%3Dludfrrfx\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">粗暴，但有效！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">鬼畜视频？人力手搓已经OUT了，李沐老师直接用算力帮大伙搞定，效果be like：</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;margin: 40px 0px;line-height: 1.5;font-weight: bold;padding-left: 15px;word-break: break-all !important;border-left-width: 6px !important;border-left-style: solid !important;border-left-color: rgb(0, 153, 127) !important;font-size: 20px !important;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">沐神教你手搓语音大模型</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统的语音和文本模型之间相互独立，李沐老师就想，欸，能不能将两者结合起来，直接让LLM用语音进行沟通。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">那么首先就要知道文本语言模型的本质是用给定的一段指令去生成预测结果，就是将任务先拆解为</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);\"><span leaf=\"\">系统指令</span></strong><em style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\"><span leaf=\"\">（system）</span></em><span leaf=\"\">、</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);\"><span leaf=\"\">用户输入</span></strong><em style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\"><span leaf=\"\">（user）</span></em><span leaf=\"\">、</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);\"><span leaf=\"\">模型回复</span></strong><em style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\"><span leaf=\"\">（assistant）</span></em><span leaf=\"\">三个部分。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">system告诉模型，需要做什么事情，例如回答该问题、写一段文字或者其他，user就是告知事情的详细内容，例如问题具体是什么、文字要什么风格。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以如果要让模型支持语音，就需要为模型增加一个系统命令，在user里输入要转录为语音的文字，让模型从system里输出对应语音数据。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样语音任务就能转换成相同的处理格式，直接打通语音和文本之间的映射，通过追加更多的数据和算力，直接</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);\"><span leaf=\"\">scaling law</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">“大力出奇迹”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: center;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100328253\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.4777777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;padding: 0px;\" data-width=\"3065\" data-height=\"1464\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.xlab.app/img-proxy/?k=410d0bdc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYicUhk5aAGtClBf0EpJYZGRRarWCicQkpMjKrMN8AvUCgk9aN6Od0gSUXGH6RZPA21oTSDGxvC7xVyUAJhwtlgOg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26randomid%3Dq7ne99mx\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就引出了新的问题，</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);\"><span leaf=\"\">语音信号本质是连续的，要如何才能在离散的文本token中表示呢？</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">现有的方法是将一秒的语音信号裁切成多段</span><em style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\"><span leaf=\"\">（如100毫秒一段）</span></em><span leaf=\"\">，为每一段匹配最相似的预定义模板</span><em style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\"><span leaf=\"\">（如45个模板）</span></em><span leaf=\"\">，然后将其表示为长度为10的编号序列，也就是一个个token。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">但这样做，虽然可以将一小时的音频从60兆压缩到0.16兆，但质量相当糟糕，所以需要</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);\"><span leaf=\"\">优先保留语音的语义信息</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，而声学信号只保留少量部分，后续再通过其他手段还原。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">于是他们训练了一个统一的离散化音频分词器，以每秒25帧的速度运行，同时保持甚至提高音频质量，以捕获语义和声学特征。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: center;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100328252\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.2759259259259259\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;padding: 0px;\" data-width=\"2499\" data-height=\"690\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.xlab.app/img-proxy/?k=505bf1ae&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYicUhk5aAGtClBf0EpJYZGRRarWCicQkpMSvJq4ax5U1QrRLELZmtxOv9PF1K6R8ptPCbmRRhEsMpMDmxibgzcWGA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26randomid%3Dnvo1v1wf\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后要让模型很好地理解和生成声音，就需要利用模型的文本空间，将语音的语义尽量地映射回文本，当中需要大量的数据支持。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">由于版权问题，沐导没有使用B站或YouTube这类公开视频网站数据，而是购买或从允许抓取的网站获取。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样得到的数据质量参差不齐，需要删除其中的90%才能满足</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);\"><span leaf=\"\">1000万小时</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">的训练数据需求。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">其次，将语音对话表示为相应的system</span><em style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\"><span leaf=\"\">（场景描述、声学特征、人物特征等）</span></em><span leaf=\"\">、user</span><em style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\"><span leaf=\"\">（对话文本）</span></em><span leaf=\"\">、assistant</span><em style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\"><span leaf=\"\">（对应音频输出）</span></em><span leaf=\"\">的形式。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">由于OpenAI和谷歌一向禁止使用他们的模型输出再训练，且训练成本过高，为了实现这种标注，他们利用相同的模型架构额外训练出一个语音模型</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);\"><span leaf=\"\">AudioVerse</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">该模型接收用户语音输入，分析并输出场景、人物、情绪、内容等信息，再将输出反过来作为生成模型的system提示和user输入，实现模型的共同进步。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">举个例子就是，如果想要教一个徒弟同时会拳脚功夫，但师傅一次又教不了，那就同时教两个徒弟，一个学打拳，一个学踢腿，然后让他们俩天天互相打，打着打着两个就都会拳脚功夫了。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">最终，这个多模态模型就完成了，不仅可以完成简单的文本转语音，还能实现更复杂的任务，比如让它写一首歌并唱出来，再加上配乐。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">还能根据语音分析场景、人物</span><em style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\"><span leaf=\"\">（性别、年龄、情绪状态）</span></em><span leaf=\"\">、环境音</span><em style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\"><span leaf=\"\">（室内外）</span></em><span leaf=\"\">，并进行复杂的理解和推理。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">在实时语音聊天上，还可实现低延迟、理解情绪并表达情绪的自然语音交互，而不仅仅是机械的问答。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">在</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);\"><span leaf=\"\">EmergentTTS-Eval</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">基准上，相较于其他模型，性能可以说是遥遥领先，尤其是在“情绪”和“问题”类别中，相比</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);\"><span leaf=\"\">GPT-4o-mini-tts</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">高出了75.7%和55.7%的胜率。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，它在Seed-TTS Eval和情感语音数据集</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(143, 143, 143);min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;(ESD)&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">等传统TTS基准测试中也取得了最佳性能。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: center;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100328262\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.49537037037037035\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;padding: 0px;\" data-width=\"7140\" data-height=\"3539\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.xlab.app/img-proxy/?k=6cf5fc96&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYicUhk5aAGtClBf0EpJYZGRRarWCicQkpMmktnkZiaXVMb0JAVn6QBXMoYflqibvt77ibJjsagamzssa8U8L95wH5MA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26randomid%3Dyprsemno\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);\"><span leaf=\"\">那么，我们能玩吗？</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">相信同学们都已经跃跃欲试了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">放心，沐导都包圆了，模型代码都已全部发布在</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);\"><span leaf=\"\">GitHub</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">上</span><em style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\"><span leaf=\"\">（可点击文末链接获取～）</span></em><span leaf=\"\">，并提供了在线试玩平台和Hugging Face版本。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: center;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100328257\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.4111111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;padding: 0px;\" data-width=\"2066\" data-height=\"850\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.xlab.app/img-proxy/?k=872e5682&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYicUhk5aAGtClBf0EpJYZGRRarWCicQkpM4MPG8IlXhoBtIFqaMUsyYbxaa7XM0aNu3DDz4PPohOVu1e8e7qzPSg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26randomid%3Diwaos1su\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">想要安装在自己电脑上的同学，需要准备好</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);\"><span leaf=\"\">GPU版Pytorch</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，或使用media驱动提供的</span><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;color: rgb(0, 153, 127);\"><span leaf=\"\">Docker</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">简化安装，readme里还有一些语音样例</span><em style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\"><span leaf=\"\">（包含文本和对应的音频）</span></em><span leaf=\"\">，大家可以自行体验学习。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">尤其是喜欢搞搞鬼畜视频、虚拟主播的同学们，这个模型一定要试试，它可以直接复制特定人物的声音。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过温馨提醒，生成特定场景的文本时，最好提供类似场景中人物说话的语音信息</span><em style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\"><span leaf=\"\">（例如吵架、放松、大笑的语音）</span></em><span leaf=\"\">，可以更好地进行声纹克隆嗷～</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin: 20px 16px !important;\"><em style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdg1v2d0pir\"><span leaf=\"\">视频教程：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mdg1v2d0ws7\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\"><a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1LGbozkEDY\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1LGbozkEDY</a></span></em></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Arial;font-variant-ligatures: normal;orphans: 2;widows: 2;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;margin-top: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;line-height: 2 !important;min-height: 1.5em !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-right: 16px !important;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px !important;\"><em style=\"color: rgb(143, 143, 143);\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mdg1v2d0sb8\"><span leaf=\"\">模型代码：<a href=\"https://github.com/boson-ai/higgs-audio\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/boson-ai/higgs-audio</a></span></span></em></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "李沐团队发布了 Higgs Audio V2 多模态语音大模型，该模型能深度理解并生成语音，并已开源提供给开发者。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "李沐团队发布了 Higgs Audio V2 多模态语音大模型，该模型能深度理解并生成语音，并已开源提供给开发者。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了李沐团队最新发布的 Higgs Audio V2 多模态语音大模型，该模型创新性地将 1000 万小时语音数据整合到 LLM 文本训练中，使其能同时理解和生成语音。它不仅能处理常规语音任务，还具备生成多种语言对话、自动韵律调整、克隆声音哼唱及同时生成语音和背景音乐等罕见能力。文章阐述了模型通过将语音任务转换为文本指令格式，并采用统一离散化音频分词器来表示连续语音信号的关键技术。为解决大规模高质量数据标注问题，团队训练了辅助模型 AudioVerse 实现自训练。Higgs Audio V2 在多项基准测试中表现优异，且已开源，提供 GitHub 代码、在线试玩平台和 Hugging Face 版本，极大降低了开发者和爱好者的使用门槛。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Higgs Audio V2 通过将海量语音数据整合至 LLM 文本训练，实现了文本与语音的深度融合。",
      "explanation": "模型创新性地将语音信号转换为 LLM 可处理的离散 token，并利用系统指令、用户输入、模型回复的统一格式，使 LLM 能同时处理文本和语音任务，实现“大力出奇迹”的扩展性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "模型具备多语言、多说话人、情感表达及背景音乐生成等高级语音能力。",
      "explanation": "Higgs Audio V2 在传统语音任务基础上，提供了多语种自然对话、韵律自适应、声音克隆哼唱、语音与背景音乐同步生成等独特功能，极大拓展了语音 AI 的应用边界。"
    },
    {
      "point": "团队通过自训练模型 AudioVerse 解决了大规模高质量语音数据标注难题。",
      "explanation": "面对版权和成本限制，团队训练了 AudioVerse 模型，通过分析用户语音输入反向生成标注信息，实现了生成模型与标注模型的共同进步，确保了训练数据的质量和规模。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Higgs Audio V2 在多项语音基准测试中性能显著超越现有模型。",
      "explanation": "模型在 EmergentTTS-Eval 等基准测试中，尤其在情绪和问题类别上，胜率远超 GPT-4o-mini-tts，并在传统 TTS 测试中也取得最佳性能，展现了其卓越的语音理解和生成能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "模型代码和试玩平台已开源，极大降低了开发者和爱好者的使用门槛。",
      "explanation": "李沐团队将 Higgs Audio V2 的核心代码发布在 GitHub，并提供在线试玩平台和 Hugging Face 版本，方便用户快速体验、学习和集成，促进了技术的普及和应用。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "李沐老师终于带着他的手搓语音大模型教程回归了....",
    "整个过程堪称**“大力出奇迹”** ，直接将**1000 万小时** 的语音数据整合到 LLM 的文本训练，让它能听也能说。",
    "如果想要教一个徒弟同时会拳脚功夫，但师傅一次又教不了，那就同时教两个徒弟，一个学打拳，一个学踢腿，然后让他们俩天天互相打，打着打着两个就都会拳脚功夫了。",
    "在**EmergentTTS-Eval** 基准上，相较于其他模型，性能可以说是遥遥领先，尤其是在“情绪”和“问题”类别中，相比**GPT-4o-mini-tts** 高出了 75.7%和 55.7%的胜率。",
    "放心，沐导都包圆了，模型代码都已全部发布在**GitHub** 上*（可点击文末链接获取～）* ，并提供了在线试玩平台和 Hugging Face 版本。"
